Anh - Anh
bedsit
(also bedsitter or bed-sitting room)
■ noun Brit. a rented room consisting of a combined bedroom and living room, with cooking facilities.

sentences.vi: Phòng đơn cho thuê £500 mỗi tháng.

sentences.en: Bedsit to let: suit student or young professional.
